[[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]] had a '''village drum''' that an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] could sound to alert to whole village of any threat.

[[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] once used the drum when his [[Ewok battle wagon|battle wagon]] was stolen by the [[Dulok/Legends|Duloks]].

